      "The ownership structure matters. Daniel and Rohaise Rose-Bristow have run the hotel for over twenty years and live on site. This is a hands-on family-owned property in a category where family ownership has become rare. Staff turnover is unusually low (some staff have been at the hotel since the 1990s), which produces a specific operational continuity.",
